Products.RichDescription: Tender, marinated Australian chicken in a rich & creamy tomato based sauce infused with a traditional blend of tandoori spices. Served with fluffy long grain rice. We've made this aromatic curry with a blend of herbs & spices including garam masala, fenugreek leaves & cardamom mixed with Australian cream & yoghurt. Our Story - We use chicken from Australian RSPCA Approved farms that are regularly assessed against the RSPCA's detailed standards, for better animal welfare.

Products.FullDescription: Woolworths Lamb Rogan Josh With Rice
Products.RichDescription:
Australian lamb marinated and slow cooked for flavour and tenderness in ginger & garam masala, in a rich tomato sauce infused with an aromatic blend of warming spices. Served with fluffy long grain rice.

This aromatic sauce has been made from scratch with a fragrant blend of spices and Australian yoghurt.

Our Story
The Australian lamb used in this recipe has been slow cooked for a perfectly tender meat and marinated with ginger & garam masala for a rich & aromatic flavour.

AdditionalAttributes.description:

Our Story
The Australian lamb used in this recipe has been slow cooked for a perfectly tender meat and marinated with ginger & garam masala for a rich & aromatic flavour.
